t: "aldhyn ataynahum altawrat wal'injyl, yaerifun mhmdana salaa allah ealayh wasalam bsfath almktwbt eindahum kmerfthm abna'hm, fkma 'ana 'abna'ahum la yashtabihun 'amamahum bghyrhm, fkdhlk muhamad salaa allah ealayh wasalam la yushtabah bghyrh ldqt wasafah fi ktbhm, wlknhm atabaeuu ahwa'hm, fkhsru 'anfusahum hin kafaruu bmhmd salaa allah ealayh wasalam wabima ja' bh"